{"title":"Päevakreem","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"organic-day-cream-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic day cream to deliver long-lasting hydration, leaving the skin soft and smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic apricot kernel oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of chamomile (soothing), pansy (protecting) and arnica (anti-inflammatory).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into freshly cleansed skin and neck. Use it in the morning and evening and whenever your skin needs natural hydration. Perfect as make-up base.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Cetyl Alcohol*, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Viola Tricolor Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Geraniol**\/***, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (85,3%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093435031879,"sku":null,"price":52.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-day-cream-50ml-714190.jpg?v=1739897338"},{"product_id":"norrskin-highly-nourishing-face-cream-50ml","title":"NorrSkin Highly Nourishing Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishes \u0026amp; moisturises, supports hydro lipid barrier in the skin. Soothing effect, prevents skin irritation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisibly improves skin texture in 14 days (confirmed by clinical tests)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeeply nourishes with power of Niacinamide and Linseed\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrevents skin dryness and dehydration with plant derived squalane\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRich in vitamins and minerals (calcium, magnesium \u0026amp; Zinc)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt soothes skin and prevents irritations\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSqualane\u003c\/span\u003e protects the skin from water loss. Deeply moisturises the skin, has a mild formula, making it suitable for sensitive skin, regulates production of sebum, has a strong anti-aging effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNiacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e, also knows as Vitamin B3 and strong antioxidant, has a cleaning, detoxifying and brightening properties. Decreases redness and irritations on the skin. Stimulates elasticity.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Oil\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing lipid barrier.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e96,3% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount of the cream on your face and neck. Gently massage the cream into the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Squalane, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetearyl Olivate, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Cetearyl Alcohol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Niacinamide, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Arginine, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Oryza Sativa Bran Wax, Centella Asiatica Root Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Stearic Acid, Lactic Acid, Parfum, Xanthan Gum, Hydroxyacetophenone, Sodium Phytate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Linalool, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308376498503,"sku":null,"price":35.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-highly-nourishing-face-cream-50ml-799906.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"hej-sensitive-24h-cream-50ml","title":"HEJ Organic Organic Sensitive 24h Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSimply a delicate all-rounder that provides intensive moisture and ensures radiant skin. Rich and quickly absorbed texture ensures that the skin feels pleasant, no matter what time of day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePromotes the balance of your skin barrier and deeply hydrates\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eQuickly absorbed texture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural power active ingredient complex made from hemp oil, oat and chamomile extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Especially for sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAllergen-reduced perfume oil, 100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHemp Oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains important Omega-6 fatty acids, promotes cell regeneration and protects the skin without feeling greasy.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOat Extract\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-inflammatory and calming effect and is particularly suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eChamomile Flower Water\u003c\/span\u003e has soothing and antibacterial characteristics and provides intensive hydration to the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to your face morning and evening after cleansing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cetearyl Alcohol, Distarch Phosphate, Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil*, Hydrogenated Rapeseed Oil, Candelilla Cera, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract*, Hypericum Perforatum Extract*, Avena Sativa Kernel Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Alcohol, Tocopherol, Citric Acid, Parfum** *ingredients from certified organic agriculture, **natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49509036327239,"sku":"","price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-organic-sensitive-24h-face-cream-50ml-375353.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"hej-reactivator-face-fluid-cactus-50ml","title":"HEJ Organic The Reactivator Face Fluid Cactus 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Face Fluid pampers you and your skin, provides long-lasting moisture and ensures a unique, light care experience after daily cleansing. Prickly pear seed oil and argan oil also protect your skin from external influences and make a valuable contribution to a fresh, young complexion.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLightweight moisturizer\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eQuickly absorbed texture that does not overload oily skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIdeal base for make-up\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Any skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePrickly Pear Oil\u003c\/span\u003e helps to regenerate the cells and keeps your skin youthful.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePrickly Pear Blossom Water\u003c\/span\u003e brings a combination of essential fatty acids to your skin care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eArgan Oil\u003c\/span\u003e is the Moroccan secret to smooth, soft skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eGrapefruit Extract\u003c\/span\u003e is a natural antibiotic to promote clear skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to face morning and evening after cleansing. Also suitable as a base under make-up\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Flower Extract*, Glycine Soja Oil*, Caprylic\/ Capric Triglyceride, Glycerin, Isoamyl Laurate, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil*, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil*, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil*, Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract*, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Amorphophallus Konjac Root Extract*, Mangifera Indica Seed Butter*, Cetyl Alcohol, Levulinic Acid, Acacia Senegal Gum, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Glyceryl Caprylate, Sodium Hyaluronate, p-Anisic Acid, Parfum**, Citral**, Citronellol**, Limonene**, Linalool** *ingredients from certified organic agriculture, **natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49596582920519,"sku":null,"price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-reactivator-face-fluid-cactus-50ml-829555.png?v=1739897251"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser","title":"MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Moisturiser 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis lightweight moisturiser improves the hydration of sensitive, easily irritated, redness-prone skin. Biotechnologically obtained molecules of seaweed work to balance the skin's microbiome and reinforce its natural protection against external stressors. Minimises the appearance of redness and burning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin daily. Use in combination with MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Night Cream for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Glycerin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium PCA, Coco- Caprylate, Isoamyl Laurate, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Aqua, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Octyldodecanol, Xanthan Gum, Cellulose, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858966782279,"sku":"","price":39.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-643317.jpg?v=1739897262"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-hydra-recharge-cream-50ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS Hydra Recharge Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eSOS Hydra Recharge Cream, intense moisture-locking cream infused with age-defying antioxidants of peony, linseed and hyaluronic acid. Hydrates, replenishes and calms dehydrated and stressed skin to restore youthful radiance. Acting as a protective layer against environmental damage, this soft-textured cream reduces the look of fine lines, and promotes optimal hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin every morning and evening or whenever your skin feels thirsty or stressed. For the best results, use in combination with SOS Hydra Repair Intensive Serum.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Glyceryl Stearate, Behenyl Alcohol, Isoamyl Laurate, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Aroma, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Cellulose, Sodium anisate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Lactic Acid, Glycine Soja Sterols, Linum Usitatissimum (Flax) Seed Extract, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Xanthan Gum, Paeonia Lactiflora (Peony) Root Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Tocopherol, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol, Geraniol, Benzyl Salicylate, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49859035300167,"sku":null,"price":37.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-hydra-recharge-cream-50ml-242361.jpg?v=1739897239"},{"product_id":"madara-spf30-plant-stem-cell-age-defying-face-sunscreen-40ml","title":"MÁDARA SPF30 Plant Stem Cell Age-Defying Face Sunscreen 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eIngredients from natural origin meet cellular biology to create this break-through daily sunscreen that provides high level protection with an invisible, flawless nude skin finish. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eInnovative formula with patent pending stem cells from Northern Dragonhead deliver a hyper dose of antioxidants to completely shield the skin from urban pollution while also regenerating and protecting the skin microbiome for an age-defying effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eThe ultra-light, subtly tinted texture infused with hyaluronic acid and SPF-boosting raspberry seed oil glides onto the skin easily, leaving no white marks. Utmost protection for a forever sun kissed look.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over your daily moisturiser. Reapply if necessary during the day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zinc Oxide, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Lecithin, Polyglyceryl-3 ricinoleate, Glycerin, Butylene Glycol, Sorbitan olivate, Aqua, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil, Vegetable Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Rhus Succedanea Fruit Wax, Hydrated Silica, Aroma, Sodium Chloride, Xanthan Gum, Sorbitan Caprylate, Jojoba Esters, Citric acid, Propanediol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Dracocephalum Ruyschiana (Dragonhead) Cell Culture Extract, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Rubus Idaeus (Raspberry) Seed Oil, Caprylyl glycol, Benzoic Acid, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), Sodium phytate, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Extract, Isostearic Acid, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Sodium Benzoate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Potassium Sorbate, Propylene Glycol, Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Citral, Linalool, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887709102407,"sku":null,"price":32.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-spf30-plant-stem-cell-age-defying-face-sunscreen-40ml-514512.jpg?v=1739897254"},{"product_id":"madara-hydra-derm-balancing-fluid-40ml","title":"MÁDARA Hydra-Derm Balancing Fluid 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis light-weight face moisturiser intensely hydrates and balances, ensuring lasting comfort and helping to improve the condition of problem-prone skin. Helps to tighten pores and minimise the appearance of breakouts.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFormulated with moisturising hyaluronic acid and fermented polysaccharides that regulate the microbiome for a clear and healthy-looking complexion. Juniper stem sells and extracts of lichen and mate tea deliver strong soothing and antioxidant benefits. Targets both teenage and adult acne.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin every morning and night. Use in combination with other ACNE formulas for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Glycerin, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cellulose, Sodium PCA, Isoamyl Laurate, Zinc PCA, Aroma, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Propanediol, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Alcohol, Xanthan Gum, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium phytate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Rhamnose, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract, CI 77007 (Ultramarines), Glucose, Glucuronic Acid, Silica, Kaolin, Maltodextrin, CI 75815 (Chlorophyllin Copper Complex), Linalool, Citral, Limonene, Citronellol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49888070107463,"sku":"","price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-hydra-derm-balancing-fluid-40ml-855043.jpg?v=1739897240"},{"product_id":"hej-the-naked-barrier-repair-face-cream-30ml","title":"HEJ Organic Naked Barrier Repair Face Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaked is a fragrance-free skincare line with highly effective and 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Naked Barrier Repair Face Cream helps your skin build its natural barrier and protect it from environmental influences. Ceramides and ectoine strengthen your skin and support its regeneration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFermented ingredients protect your skin with valuable antioxidants and vitamins. They are particularly gentle and skin-friendly because they have been fermented in olive brine, not in alcohol. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStrengthens the natural skin barrier\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCeramides and ectoine protect against environmental influences and provide moisture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRich care that melts on the skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free and natural  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to the face, neck and décolleté morning and evening as a final treatment\u003cstrong\u003e.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (Water), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Glycerin, Betaine, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Squalane, Ectoin, Propanediol, Glyceryl Stearate, Jojoba Esters, Saccharide Isomerate, Benzyl Alcohol, Bisabolol, Xanthan Gum, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Tocopherol, Lactobacillus Ferment Lysate, Ceramide Np, Sodium Hyaluronate, Dehydroacetic Acid, Polyglycerin-3, Citric Acid, Sodium Citrate, Sodium Hydroxide \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905713246535,"sku":null,"price":17.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-naked-barrier-repair-face-cream-30ml-477281.png?v=1739897157"},{"product_id":"hej-organic-naked-instant-pore-refining-face-cream-30ml","title":"HEJ Organic Naked Instant Pore Refining Face Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaked is a fragrance-free skincare line with highly effective and 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWhether as a face cream or primer, Naked Instant Pore Refining Face Cream's natural pigments give you an even complexion. Azelaic acid has a regulating effect on sebum production, cleanses the pores and effectively prevents skin impurities. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe first Nature certified product with azelaic acid.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGives an even complexion and new elasticity\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSqualane provides moisture and protects against environmental influences\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAzelaic acid has an antibacterial effect and reduces redness and inflammation\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eParticularly suitable for impure, oily and combination skin  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free and natural \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply it to your face in the morning and evening after cleansing and massage in gently. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Glycerin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Potassium Aluminium Silicate, Caprylyl Caprylate\/Caprate, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Betaine, Acelaic Acid, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil*, Squalane, Sodium Hyaluronate, Prunus Armeniaca Fruit Extract*, Chondrus Crispus Powder, Acmella Oleracea Extract, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Benzoate, Glucomannan, CI 77891, Silica, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Sodium Anisate,Tocopherol, Sodium Hydroxide \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905759547719,"sku":null,"price":15.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-naked-instant-pore-refining-face-cream-30ml-993591.png?v=1739897167"},{"product_id":"hej-organic-the-protector-spf30-face-cream","title":"HEJ Organic The Protector SPF30 Face Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtects your skin every day and in all weathers with SPF30 and thus counteract premature skin aging. Mineral UV filter protects you from UVA and UVB rays without any whitening. The Protector Face Cream's quickly absorbed texture is light and moisturizing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLight day care with SPF30 for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral UV filter absorbs quickly without whitening\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin C and hyaluronic acid protect the skin and moisturize\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow even more sustainable: Aluminum tube (100% recyclable) for complete emptying of the product\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply me to your face, neck and décolleté in the morning, as well as every now and then if you spend a long time outdoors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Flower Extract*, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Titanium Dioxide, Glycine Soja Oil*, Glyceryl Citrate\/Lactate\/Linoleate\/Oleate, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Zinc Oxide, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil*, Pongamia Glabra Seed Oil*, Glycerin, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil*, Sodium Hyaluronate, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil*, Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract*, Tocopherol, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Sodium PCA, Sorbitol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Acacia Senegal Gum, Alumina, Lauroyl Lysine, Xanthan Gum, Levulinic Acid, Cetearyl Alcohol, p-Anisic Acid, Glyceryl Caprylate, Stearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum**, Citral**, Citronellol*, Limonene*, Linalool** \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905809551687,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-protector-spf30-face-cream-30ml-965181.png?v=1739897165"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe multitasking Naïf Nurturing Day Cream hydrates and protects face, neck and décolleté during the day from the harmful effects of UV radiation. Al this thanks to the added tomato extract. To support the natural skin process, the day cream contains natural oils, such as avocado and almond oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe day cream is quickly absorbed and you don't need much of it. That's why you'll be able to use the bioplastic tube's content even longer. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the Nurturing Day Cream evenly (you don't need much) to a cleansed face, neck and décolleté.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe natural SPF6 from tomato extract provides for protection against harmful UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed Seed) Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Solanum Lycopersicum (Tomato Fruit\/Leaf\/Stem) Extract, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary Leaf) Extract, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915540205895,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-773702.png?v=1739897170"},{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-hydrating-day-cream-50ml","title":"NURME Neroli Hydrating Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eThis moisturizing day cream provides long-lasting hydration for dry and stressed skin throughout the day. A powerful blend of antioxidants and restorative ingredients leaves the skin soft and smooth while helping to prevent signs of aging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, has strong antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it beneficial for acne-prone skin and clogged pores. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. Rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil offers anti-aging and anti-acne benefits, reducing inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eThis product is packaged in a recyclable polypropylene airless bottle. The airless packaging prevents air exposure, ensuring microbiological purity and extending the shelf life of natural cosmetics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003eApply to clean skin.  Allow to absorb completely. Can be used under makeup or alone.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua*, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Glycerin**, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Betain**, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate*, Glyceryl Stearate**, Cetearyl Alcohol**, Myristyl Myristate**, Sodium Levulinate**, Panthenol*, Sodium Anisate**, Ascorbyl Palmitate**, Benzyl Alcohol**, Lactic Acid**, Sodium Hyaluronate**, Allantoin*, Sodium Benzoate**, Tocopherol**, Potassium Sorbate**, Xanthan Gum**, Hectorite**, Cellulose**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Citrus Aurantium Flower Oil*, Limonene***, Linalool***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e* Natural origin\u003cbr\u003e**Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915909075271,"sku":null,"price":27.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-hydrating-day-cream-50ml-839981.jpg?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-50ml","title":"MÁDARA Vitamin C Illuminating Recovery Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e​Treat your skin with this glow-enhancing moisturiser that instantly revives dull and tired complexion, promoting more even skin tone. Formulated with a stabilised form of Vitamin C, a potent antioxidant, used in skincare and dermatology to brighten, improve skin tone and promote a healthy glow, it also helps to prevent hyperpigmentation and dark spots. Hyaluronic acid ensures intense hydration, whilst the seaweed extract boosts the brightening effect, leaving the skin feeling softer and smoother and looking youthfully fresh and beautifully radiant.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply daily on clean skin. Recommended to use daily or as a treatment course 2–3 times a year. Avoid direct sun exposure after the application. Use sunscreen afterwards.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Isoamyl Laurate, Betaine, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Sodium PCA, Aroma, Potassium Hydroxide, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Sodium Citrate, Xanthan Gum, Rubus Chamaemorus (Cloudberry) Fruit Extract, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascophyllum Nodosum (Brown Algae) Extract, Citric acid, CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916523835719,"sku":null,"price":40.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-50ml-305593.jpg?v=1739897158"},{"product_id":"madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Vitamin C Illuminating Recovery Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e​Treat your skin with this glow-enhancing moisturiser that instantly revives dull and tired complexion, promoting more even skin tone. Formulated with a stabilised form of Vitamin C, a potent antioxidant, used in skincare and dermatology to brighten, improve skin tone and promote a healthy glow, it also helps to prevent hyperpigmentation and dark spots. Hyaluronic acid ensures intense hydration, whilst the seaweed extract boosts the brightening effect, leaving the skin feeling softer and smoother and looking youthfully fresh and beautifully radiant.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply daily on clean skin. Recommended to use daily or as a treatment course 2–3 times a year. Avoid direct sun exposure after the application. Use sunscreen afterwards.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Isoamyl Laurate, Betaine, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Sodium PCA, Aroma, Potassium Hydroxide, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Sodium Citrate, Xanthan Gum, Rubus Chamaemorus (Cloudberry) Fruit Extract, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascophyllum Nodosum (Brown Algae) Extract, Citric acid, CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916599726407,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-15ml-419448.jpg?v=1739897174"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-day-cream-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Day Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi day cream Day is the ideal solution for daily moisturizing and protecting the skin. This silky cream soothes irritated skin, reduces redness and protects against external stressors. It restores the skin’s natural moisture balance and elasticity, leaving it looking radiant and healthy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi  Age Defence Day Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturises deeply\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes the skin soft and supple\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces redness and inflammation by soothing sensitive skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProtects the skin from external environmental factors\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e – antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e– rich in vitamins A and E. Helps reduce wrinkles and improve skin elasticity, stimulating collagen production and cell renewal.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor dry and normal skin. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Aleurites Moluccana seed oil (Kukui nut oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil).\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042340372807,"sku":"","price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-day-cream-30ml-221611.png?v=1739897155"},{"product_id":"berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Light Natural Glow Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover Berrichi face cream Light – natural radiance and balance for your skin. Face cream Light is a light and silky cream designed to moisturise and protect combination and normal skin on a daily basis. It helps to restore the skin’s natural moisture balance, evens the texture and supports the skin’s natural defences, leaving skin radiant and soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Light Natural Glow Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight and fast-absorbing texture that does not clog pores\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturising action that restores the skin’s moisture balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritations and soothes inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnti-ageing\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cu\u003eFurcellaran\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/u\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRough Razor Beard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– with antibacterial properties, it helps soothe and protect the skin, promoting a smoother, brighter complexion.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor combined and normal skin\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Helianthus Annuus Seed oil\/Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate\/Usnea Barbata extract (Usnea Barbata), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042379202887,"sku":null,"price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml-286537.png?v=1739897155"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-naokreem-meestele-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Face Cream for Men 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFace cream For Men contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which anti-aging and deep moisturizing effect has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAstaxanthin acts as if on the skin natural doping. This powerful antioxidant can penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. The humidity level balances and premature wrinkles generation decreases. The skin is protected from the attack of UV rays and free radicals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream is well suited for after-shave care.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Age Defence Face Cream for Men:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep moisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti-aging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dryness and scar tissue.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for after-shave care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith light absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran, astaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom the Amazon rainforest \u003ci\u003ecacay\u003c\/i\u003e– oil improves skin elasticity and evens skin tone. Aloe soothes and relieves irritations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, ), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Glycerin**, Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042419835207,"sku":null,"price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-30ml-969154.png?v=1739897169"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-day-cream-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Day Cream REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi day cream Day is the ideal solution for daily moisturizing and protecting the skin. This silky cream soothes irritated skin, reduces redness and protects against external stressors. It restores the skin’s natural moisture balance and elasticity, leaving it looking radiant and healthy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi  Age Defence Day Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturises deeply\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes the skin soft and supple\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces redness and inflammation by soothing sensitive skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProtects the skin from external environmental factors\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e – antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e– rich in vitamins A and E. Helps reduce wrinkles and improve skin elasticity, stimulating collagen production and cell renewal.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor dry and normal skin. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Aleurites Moluccana seed oil (Kukui nut oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil).\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084266996039,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-day-cream-refill-30ml-412866.png?v=1739979949"},{"product_id":"berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Light Natural Glow Cream REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover Berrichi face cream Light – natural radiance and balance for your skin. Face cream Light is a light and silky cream designed to moisturise and protect combination and normal skin on a daily basis. It helps to restore the skin’s natural moisture balance, evens the texture and supports the skin’s natural defences, leaving skin radiant and soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Light Natural Glow Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight and fast-absorbing texture that does not clog pores\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturising action that restores the skin’s moisture balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritations and soothes inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnti-ageing\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cu\u003eFurcellaran\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/u\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRough Razor Beard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– with antibacterial properties, it helps soothe and protect the skin, promoting a smoother, brighter complexion.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor combined and normal skin\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Helianthus Annuus Seed oil\/Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate\/Usnea Barbata extract (Usnea Barbata), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084305465671,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-refill-30ml-453681.png?v=1739979948"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Face Cream for Men REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFace cream For Men contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which anti-aging and deep moisturizing effect has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAstaxanthin acts as if on the skin natural doping. This powerful antioxidant can penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. The humidity level balances and premature wrinkles generation decreases. The skin is protected from the attack of UV rays and free radicals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream is well suited for after-shave care.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Age Defence Face Cream for Men:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep moisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti-aging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dryness and scar tissue.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for after-shave care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith light absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran, astaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom the Amazon rainforest \u003ci\u003ecacay\u003c\/i\u003e– oil improves skin elasticity and evens skin tone. Aloe soothes and relieves irritations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, ), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Glycerin**, Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084323389767,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml-844196.png?v=1739979950"},{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-face-moisturiser-with-vitamin-e-aloe-vera-travel-size-30ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Face Moisturiser with Vitamin E + Aloe Vera - Travel Size 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis multi award-winning vegan face moisturiser is suitable for all skin types. Vitamin E rich argan powder is combined with skin-soothing cocoa butter, aloe vera and blood orange.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspiring, upcycling, uplifting: This dermatologically approved face cream is made with finely-ground powder of discarded argan shells, a natural by-product of the argan oil industry and rich in antioxidant Vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWinner of the \"Responsible Beauty\" award in the CEW Awards 2022, \"Best Moisturiser\" in the Natural Health Beauty Awards 2021. Winner in the Beauty Shortlist Awards 2021.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn UpCircle Bestseller now perfectly packaged into a 30ml travel friendly format, great for any getaway.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean, dry skin. Massage in until the cream absorbs. Suitable for all skin types and for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glycerin, C14-22 Alcohols, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Coffea Arabica (Coffee) Seed Extract, Acer Rubrum (Maple) Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Calendula Officinalis Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Extract*, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Hydroxide, C12-20 Alkyl Glucoside, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Salicylic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene**. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organically grown ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural constituent of essential oils listed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133263118663,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-face-moisturiser-with-vitamin-e-aloe-vera-travel-size-30ml-234246.png?v=1740808672"},{"product_id":"bee-it-face-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing and anti-age prevention face cream, with a soft and light texture, easy to apply. It has professional efficacy with 100% natural origin active ingredients NaturOxygen® and Pentavitin® EcoCert, Cosmos and Natrue certified, which increase metabolism and skin turnover, making the skin nourished, radiant and even younger. Enriched with Sodium Hyaluronate, Shea butter, Vitamin E, propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply and massage with circular movements to regenerate the skin, releasing your emotions.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Cetearyl alcohol, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Cetearyl glucoside, Sorbitan olivate, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum [Fragrance], Butyrospermum parkii (Shea) butter, Glycerin, Cyamopsis tetragonoloba (guar) gum, Tocopheryl acetate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Citric acid, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Saccharide isomerate, Hydroxycitronellal, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Saccharomyces lysate, Disodium succinate, Sodium citrate, Glutamic acid, Glycine, Threonine, Valine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245337014599,"sku":null,"price":10.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-face-cream-50ml-9846172.png?v=1756636044"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-rich-hydra-barrier-cica-cream-40ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS Rich Hydra-Barrier CICA Cream 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eInstantly sooth and comfort very dry, dehydrated, stressed and reactive skin with this rich hydra-barrier cream. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with the hydrating and calming Centella Asiatica (CICA) extract to bolster skin’s protective barrier and help restore the epidermal balance. Hyaluronic acid, soothing bisabolol, nurturing shea butter and repairing ceramides in the formulation help to improve moisture retention, prevent dryness-induced discomfort and signs of premature ageing. Works to diminish the feeling of taut and itchy skin and unveils a better-looking complexion by promoting skin’s healthy radiance.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a generous amount to clean skin. Use in the morning and night or whenever your skin feels dry, taut and stressed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e ALOE BARBADENSIS (ALOE) LEAF JUICE*; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL*; GLYCERIN; THEOBROMA CACAO (COCOA) SEED BUTTER*; CETEARYL ALCOHOL; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; POLYGLYCERYL-3 STEARATE; BETAINE; SODIUM PCA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE; ISOAMYL LAURATE; OCTYLDODECANOL; AROMA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; AQUA; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; XANTHAN GUM; BISABOLOL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; PAEONIA LACTIFLORA (PEONY) ROOT EXTRACT; BORAGO OFFICINALIS (BORAGE) SEED OIL*; CELLULOSE; GLYCOSPHINGOLIPIDS; LACTIC ACID; OENOTHERA BIENNIS (EVENING PRIMROSE) OIL*; RUBUS IDAEUS (RASPBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; SODIUM PHYTATE; CENTELLA ASIATICA (PENNYWORT) LEAF EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; TOCOPHEROL; HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID; SODIUM HYALURONATE; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***; CITRONELLOL**; GERANIOL**; BENZYL SALICYLATE**; EUGENOL**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e27% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52919609229639,"sku":null,"price":37.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-rich-hydra-barrier-cica-cream-40ml-2135696.jpg?v=1765327460"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/paevakreem.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}